#Kai
I know a beautiful hill where we can see the stars at night. Do you want to come with me?[p]
There's something i need to tell you."[p]
We visit the hill that weekend. Where the grass field is endless and the sky looks like a magical curtain of lights.[p]
The scene brought a smile on my face but Kai...there's something wrong with him. [p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
