#Kai
An...i'll tell you everything. Everything i've been hiding from you.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Kai isn't my only name in Hell. I'm known as the Bloody Prince, the strongest Death's Messenger.[p]
And because of that, i grew arrogant. A thousand years ago i started killing people for the sake of it. To get more souls, become more powerful.[p]
Until i met and fell in love with an exorcist girl named Anna. But i...i considered it as a weakness.[p]
I massacred her entire family. And before i could kill her, Hell King appeared, put an amber necklace on Anna and gave me a curse: from now till the rest of eternity, i have to watch over the girl with this necklace, no matter how many times she reincarnates...That's...that's how i knew so much about you.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
