[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
Part of me already knew it. The way this necklace mysteriously appeared on my neck since the day i was born and i can't take it off. The way it shined when you first appeared in front of me.[p]
But you...you who have been chasing another girl for a thousand years. Maybe Anna might appreciate such an undying love, too bad i'm not her.[p]
And you've been watching me since i was a baby because i resembled someone else.[p]
From the beginning i knew something was odd about the way you treated me. I thought it was because of Dr Quang's wish so i tried to stop myself from loving you but the truth is so much, so much worse.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
From the beginning it was this cruel curse that let me able to meet you. There was no hope for us.I was selfish. I hid the truth away from you because i know there's no way you can accept me when you find out.[p]
I thought that as long as i make you happy, i can use my power to lie to you forever. I made excuses for myself. That you needed me as a doctor to guide you. That you needed me to protect you, to help you getting through the pain of losing Lan, that Hoang needed us both,...[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
You're right. There's no way i would have accepted you if i knew. If i didn't love you so much i would be disgusted by you right now.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

