[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
An, i admit, i've never been able to erase Anna out of my heart. She's the reason i fought so hard for a human life.[p]
But from the bottom of my heart, i never lied when i said i want you to be happy. Not because of Anna or the necklace.[p]
You, the girl who fought for what you believed what's right even when you got backlash from it.[p]
It's your smile that saved me. It was you who lifted the curse from me.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
