I would have died that day if you didn't come. You've been protecting me, guiding me, taking care of me since the day we first met.[p]
You put trust in me, helped me achieve my dream,... You gave me love when i needed it the most. Even now, i'm still glad i met you.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

