[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
I can't be here if it wasn't for this man. And yet why do we have to keep hurting each others like this?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Didn't i know this from the beginning? That i can never fill his eternity.[p]
That there's no way to fill all the imbalance in power, time, memories,...between us.[p]
Today will come sooner or later. Meanwhile i kept lying to myself and cling on him,[p]
But Kai, i'll show you that dying here isn't your only choice. I'll save you. There are so much people that need you more than me.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

