[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
It's ok. The only reason why you managed to reincarnate so many times was because of the necklace.[p]
You're an exception of nature, you existed alongside with me. I was your Death's Messenger for the last 1000 years and you paid no price for what you wished.[p]
But now that the curse is lifted, it's not the case anymore. I won't be able to find you and other Death's Messengers will definitely take the soul charge.[p]
Beside, it's not fair to stop you from getting your wishes. And you won't remember me in your next lives either.[p]
Don't mind those dreams of mine. All we have is the present...[p]
[_tb_end_text]

