[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Even when this is good bye, what matters is everything we had. Thank you for showing me what love is. Thank you for taking care of me till the very end.[p]
This is the last time you'll see me and i won't be watching over you no more.[p]
I'll continue the old doctor's wish as "Quang" in a place far away from here and leave the hospital to someone else. [p]
I'll leave you the mansion as it still contains memories with Hoang that i know you want to keep. I'll take the necklace and that eye's ability to see the black feathers with me. [p]
You don't have to burden yourself about telling people's their final day anymore. So please remember, even when you can't see me, somewhere, someone in this world will always love you. [p]
Someone will always root for you. Someone will always believe that you can make it. You're never alone.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

