[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Kai reach out to me shakingly. As if he's scared he's gonna break me with every sudden movement his fingers make.[p]
As if he's scared that this is wrong. I close my eyes, waiting for a kiss.[p]
But all that's left is the summer wind blowing through my cheek, drying the tears and the sound of the wings flying away. The necklace already disappeared.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
So i fall down and burst down in tears, cry like i have never cried before.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
...I love you...[p]
I love you, i love you, i love you so much...and in the end, i couldn't even use honest words to say it.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Goodbye to the man that showed me the beauty of all the pains that life can bring, that life is still beautiful even when it shows its most cruel side.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Goodbye...my dearest.[p]
Till we meet again, when we're both free from the black feathers.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

